⚙️ Installation Requirements for Timetable Generator App

                                1️⃣ Software / Tools

| Tool / Software                 | Version / Notes       | Purpose                              |
| ------------------------------- | --------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| Python                          | 3.10 or higher        | Main programming language            |
| MySQL                           | 8.0 or higher         | Database management                  |
| MySQL Workbench (optional)      | Latest version        | GUI to view and manage database      |
| Git                             | Latest stable version | Version control / GitHub integration |
| VS Code / PyCharm / Sublime     | Any modern editor     | Code editing                         |
| pip                             | Latest                | Python package manager               |
